quran[4{c,v,t}:
2,187,"tumahray liye rozon ke zamane mein raton ko apni biwion ke paas jana halal kar diya gaya hai woh tumahray liye libaas hain aur tum unn ke liye Allah ko maloom ho gaya ke tum log chupkay chupkay apne aap se khayanat kar rahay thay, magar aُ seen ne tumhara qasoor maaf kar diya aur tum se dar guzar farmaya ab tum apni biwion ke sath shab bashi karo aur jo lutaf Allah ne tumahray liye jaaiz kar diya hai, ussay haasil karo neez raton ko khao piyo yahan taq ke tum ko siyahi shab ki dahari sesupaidah سپیدۂ subah ki dahari numaya nazar aa jaye tab yeh sab kaam chore kar raat taq apna roza poora karo aur jab tum masjidoon meinmo'a-takifho, to biwion se mubashrat nah karo yeh Allah ki baandhi hui hade hain, un ke qareeb nah phatakna iss terhan Allah apne ehkaam logon ke liye Busrahat bayan karta hai, tawaqqa hai ke woh ghalat ravayye se bachchen ge"
2,188,aur tum log nah to aapas mein aik dosray ke maal naarwa tareeqa se khao aur nah hakmon ke agay un ko is gharz ke liye paish karo ke tumhe dosaron ke maal ka koi hissa qasdan zalimana tareeqay se khanay ka mauqa mil jaye
2,189,log tum se chaand ki ghatti barhti sooraton ke mutaliq puchhte hain kaho : yeh logon ke liye tarikhon ki taayun ki aur hajj ki alamtain hain neez un se kaho : yeh koi neki ka kaam nahi hai ke apne gharon mein peechay ki taraf daakhil hotay ho neki to asal mein yeh hai ke aadmi Allah ki narazi se bachay lehaza tum apne gharon mein darwazay hi se aaya karo Albata Allah se drtay raho shayad ke tumhe Falah naseeb ho jaye
2,190,"aur tum Allah ki raah mein unn logon se lrho, jo tum se lartay hain, magar zayad-ti nah karo ke Allah zayad-ti karne walon ko pasand nahi karta"
